        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Common questions about our sponsorship opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
